text: Beykeyevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Starokurmashevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 170 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Kushnarenkovo, 20 km from Starokurmashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Beykeyevo
